Ask HN: How to Moneytize TUI Tools?
text:
I do think tui tools are more productive for developers vs the gui ones. They consume less resources, more configurable and can work with other tools through pipes or socks.
But seems it is pretty hard to moneytize, is there some success stories? Any idea welcomed.
